review_blob: the two on appearance is for the can..it  has a nice color scheme..as far as the beer goes.i think this stuff surpasses hamms as the king of whitetrash beer..natural ice is the cheapest beer i could find in my local convenience store..even cheaper than busch and schmidts..its a watery piss yellow it tastes like your drinking a mixture of grain water and piss..disgusting...cheap..what more can you say..the worst of the worst...if you wanna get drunk for cheap grab a 40oz of big bear..dont buy this crap..ugh..youll be sorry
